  "prompt": "What is JetsTwit.com?",
  "response": "JetsTwit.com is a website that aggregates and displays X posts (tweets) related to the New York Jets, a professional American football team. The site pulls X posts from various users, including fans, journalists, and official team accounts, providing a centralized location for Jets-related content on the social media platform. \n\nThe main features of JetsTwit.com include:\n\n1. **Real-time Updates**: The site refreshes automatically to show the latest X posts about the New York Jets.\n\n2. **Search Functionality**: Users can search for specific keywords or hashtags to find relevant X posts.\n\n3. **User Accounts**: While not necessary to view content, users can create accounts to save their favorite X posts or customize their feed.\n\n4. **Embeddable Widgets**: JetsTwit.com offers widgets that can be embedded on other websites to display Jets-related X posts.\n\nThe purpose of JetsTwit.com is to provide a convenient way for New York Jets fans to stay updated on team news, player updates, and fan reactions without having to navigate through the broader X platform.",
